@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kepnub(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.07 * ((v0 + 0.62 * v0 + 0.72) / v2))
    v2 = (wp.sin(v2) * (tmp - (v2 + 1.00 + tmp + 0.84)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.68) * wp.abs(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
